{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO838901BTC1043P0D1N000531", "chronotag": "1742318923118", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "531", "numeroOrdreDepot": "531", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "AN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO838901BTC1043P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PIONANR5L17BTC1043", "triAmendement": "oeaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaag", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA335612", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845514", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"acteurRef": ["PA721896", "PA795998", "PA721270", "PA720838", "PA796106", "PA795868", "PA267306", "PA774962", "PA796010", "PA842271", "PA793174", "PA795820", "PA795240", "PA795876", "PA605745", "PA842299"]}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Lecoq,  Mme&#160;Faucillon, Mme&#160;K/Bidi, M.&#160;Peu, Mme&#160;Bourouaha, M.&#160;B&#233;nard, M.&#160;Castor, M.&#160;Chassaigne, Mme&#160;Lebon, M.&#160;Maillot, M.&#160;Maurel, M.&#160;Monnet, M.&#160;Nadeau, Mme&#160;Reid&#160;Arbelot, M.&#160;Rimane, M.&#160;Sansu et M.&#160;Tjibaou"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 22", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 22", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 22", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/1043.asp#D_Article_22"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"avant_A_Apres": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "numero": "49", "alineaDesignation": "Alin\u00e9a 49"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p>Supprimer l'alin&#x00E9;a 49.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Cet amendement vise &#x00E0; supprimer le 3&#x00B0; de l&#x2019;article L.5332-16 qui concerne les installations portuaires pr&#x00E9;sentant des risques &#x00E9;lev&#x00E9;s ne comprenant pas de zone d&#x2019;acc&#x00E8;s restreint.</p><p>En effet, la notion d&#x2019;&nbsp;&#x00AB;&nbsp;installation pr&#x00E9;sentant des risques &#x00E9;lev&#x00E9;s&nbsp;&#x00BB; est vague et floue, laissant une marge d&#x2019;appr&#x00E9;ciation trop large aux autorit&#x00E9;s charg&#x00E9;es de son application. Cette impr&#x00E9;cision peut conduire &#x00E0; des interpr&#x00E9;tations divergentes, &#x00E0; une ins&#x00E9;curit&#x00E9; juridique et &#x00E0; des in&#x00E9;galit&#x00E9;s de traitement entre les diff&#x00E9;rentes installations.</p><p>En supprimant le 3&#x00B0;, il s&#x2019;agit ainsi de limiter les exigences d&#x2019;autorisation aux zones et installations dont les enjeux op&#x00E9;rationnels et s&#x00E9;curitaires sont clairement d&#x00E9;finis (zone &#x00E0; acc&#x00E8;s restreint et installations manipulant des conteneurs) afin de permettre une meilleure application de la loi et d&#x2019;&#x00E9;viter les abus li&#x00E9;s &#x00E0; un pouvoir discr&#x00E9;tionnaire excessif.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2025-03-14", "datePublication": "2025-03-16", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "AC", "libelle": "A discuter"}, "sousEtat": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "dateSort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "sort": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO838901BTC1043P0D1N000531?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "0", "divisionCodeLoi": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}